    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so i had a small cyst removed by a doctor like 3 days ago here in sydney and the cut looks a bit weird. its kind of red and feels warm to the touch and there is some yellowish stuff oozing out of it. is that normal or should i be worried? can i just put a warm compress on it and some neosporin from the chemist to clear it up?",
