      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i was kinda worried it was an infection but it sounds like it's just part of the healing process if it's just yellow. i don't really want to drive back to the clinic and pay for another appointment if i don't have to. do you think if i just keep up with the warm compresses and the neosporin every few hours i can just manage it myself at home? i'm feeling okay otherwise, no fever or anything.",
